{"tid":1488322,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"劉業成對連登仔開始束手無策，於是問大師意見","createTime":"2019-08-19T14:57:34.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-19T16:21:55.000Z","uid":235015,"like":37,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"752875bb0863b2c02a0f9f007c35864c58cdbc40","tid":1488322,"uid":235015,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T14:57:34.000Z","msg":"劉業成對於8.18事件束手無策，於是去拜訪一位大師，請求解決方法<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n劉<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：大師，班連登仔愈黎愈醒目，愈黎愈難捉，引又引唔到，搵人扮鬼又搞唔到事，有咩計可以搞掂佢地？<br />\n<br />\n大師<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />聞言，帶左劉業成去一片大海附近，向海指左一指。<br />\n<br />\n劉<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：大師！你意思係我應該懷住大海般既胸襟，接受唔同人既意見，聆聽唔同人既聲音，大家表達到訴求，人就會自然散去？<br />\n<br />\n大師<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：屌你老母！毅進仔真係毅進仔。所謂海納百川，有容奶大。一個中下貨色大波madam 已經搞到佢地神智不清。你下次直頭搵班女警，樣唔緊要，最緊要大波，下次示威企哂係佢地前面，到時佢地自然舉手投降啦！"},{"pid":"241c1b51721d4e66b84b5d13155b5ef50957acbf","tid":1488322,"uid":241244,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T14:57:54.000Z","msg":"（整合） 818之後仲有行動㗎我地！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1487938\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1487938</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n普教中！！！救下香港嘅下一代！！！！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1475548\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1475548</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"f24d90701f66b5900a6e05ea0d75154bdfb683b9","tid":1488322,"uid":206827,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T14:58:39.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">阻阻大家 入黎擺低死線唔該<br />\n既然無死線做唔到野就擺低死線既日期出黎</span></span><br />\n<br />\n大家個個話要死線 死線呢？<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1488086\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1488086</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"89d13daa49a34314a4b53a29051f26f876e1dbd5","tid":1488322,"uid":263219,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyT